      <title>cs61A SU20_2</title>
      <link href="/2023/01/09/cs61A%20SU20-2/"/>
      <url>/2023/01/09/cs61A%20SU20-2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#定义函数：</span><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>name<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>formal parameters<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token keyword">return</span> expression<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># high-order function:</span><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">delay</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>arg<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'delayed'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">g</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> arg    <span class="token keyword">return</span> gdelay<span class="token punctuation">(</span>delay<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 输出结果</span>delayeddelayed <span class="token number">6</span></code></pre><p>delay函数执行过程：<br><img>D:\CS61A\总结\delay解释.png</p><p>先执行<code>delay(delay)() return -&gt; delay</code></p><p>第一个arg == delay，delay后的第一个空括号是g函数的参数，</p><p>之后相当于<code>delay(6)() return -&gt; 6</code></p><p>第二个arg == 6, 6后的空括号是g函数的参数</p><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">pirate</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>arggg<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'matey'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">plunder</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>arggg<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> arggg    <span class="token keyword">return</span> plunderpirate<span class="token punctuation">(</span>pirate<span class="token punctuation">(</span>pirate<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">7</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 输出结果</span>mateymateyError</code></pre><pre><code>pirate(pirate(pirate))(5)(7) = pirate(plunder)(5)(7) (Matey first time) = plunder(5)(7) (Matey second time) = 5(7) (Error here)</code></pre><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">horse</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>mask<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    horse <span class="token operator">=</span> mask    <span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">mask</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>horse<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> horse    <span class="token keyword">return</span> horse<span class="token punctuation">(</span>mask<span class="token punctuation">)</span>mask <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">lambda</span> horse<span class="token punctuation">:</span> horse<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token triple-quoted-string string">"""输出结果(返回值)>>> horse(mask)2"""</span></code></pre><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python">mask 等价于 <span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">mask1</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>horse<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    res <span class="token operator">=</span> horse<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> reshorse<span class="token punctuation">(</span>mask<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">==</span> mask1<span class="token punctuation">(</span>mask<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">==</span> mask<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">==</span> <span class="token number">2</span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
